{
  "stem": "17821.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 250.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean, this dangerous thing because the Germans might have run over, run just then, when I think about it.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he gave me a lot of money, I think it was a million francs.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That scared me, and I locked it up.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the next day, I was to give it to a man who was coming who was bringing from his horse farm, bringing over the demarcation line, 40 mares that were about to foal.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was to meet this man, which I did.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then I'd done that job, that was all.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I went to see the head of the French line on which the boat I was taking on the Monday and I went on a Saturday afternoon.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I talked to him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I said, you know, my boss has all these horses.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I doubt if he'll leave them here.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He'll want to send them somewhere else.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Does the transatlantic line-- that's what he was, he was the head of the French transit-- have facilities on ships to take them to North Africa, because North Africa had areas for horses and so on.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he said, oh yes, we could do that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I said, well, OK, now I'm going to see him in New York, I'm leaving Monday.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Supposing he would rather have the ship sent to America or South America or somewhere, can you still do that?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Yes, we can do that, he said.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Oh good.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I'll know to tell him that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "By the way, I'm taking this ship on Monday, you wouldn't have a room there for my my husband?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he said, just a minute, and he inquired.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Yes, there was just one space left on that ship.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
